import React from 'react';
import { Container, Typography, Grid, Box } from '@mui/material';
import PhishingIcon from '@mui/icons-material/Phishing'; // Placeholder for a relevant icon
import LeaderboardIcon from '@mui/icons-material/Leaderboard'; // Placeholder for a relevant icon
import SetMealIcon from '@mui/icons-material/SetMeal';; // Placeholder for a relevant icon

function HighlightsSection() {
  return (
    <Container maxWidth="lg" sx={{ paddingY: 8 }}>
      <Grid container spacing={4}>
        <Grid item xs={12} md={4}>
          <Box textAlign="center">
            <PhishingIcon fontSize="large" sx={{ color: '#004d61', marginBottom: 2 }} />
            <Typography variant="h6" sx={{ color: '#006994', fontWeight: 'bold' }}>
              Trusted Tournaments
            </Typography>
            <Typography variant="body2" sx={{ color: '#6c757d' }}>
              Participate in verified online fishing tournaments and win prizes.
            </Typography>
          </Box>
        </Grid>
        <Grid item xs={12} md={4}>
          <Box textAlign="center">
            <LeaderboardIcon fontSize="large" sx={{ color: '#004d61', marginBottom: 2 }} />
            <Typography variant="h6" sx={{ color: '#006994', fontWeight: 'bold' }}>
              Real-Time Scoring
            </Typography>
            <Typography variant="body2" sx={{ color: '#6c757d' }}>
              Track your progress with real-time leaderboards.
            </Typography>
          </Box>
        </Grid>
        <Grid item xs={12} md={4}>
          <Box textAlign="center">
            <SetMealIcon fontSize="large" sx={{ color: '#004d61', marginBottom: 2 }} />
            <Typography variant="h6" sx={{ color: '#006994', fontWeight: 'bold' }}>
              Secure Payments
            </Typography>
            <Typography variant="body2" sx={{ color: '#6c757d' }}>
              Safe and reliable payment methods for prize distribution.
            </Typography>
          </Box>
        </Grid>
      </Grid>
    </Container>
  );
}

export default HighlightsSection;
